---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>GMONIT Документация</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/demo-docs/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #fff; color: #001c47; }

    .header {
      background: #001c47;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .header img { height: 36px; }
    .header span {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001c47 0%, #0d3a7a 100%);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero__grid {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
    }

    .hero__blob {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(80px);
      opacity: 0.2;
    }
    .hero__blob--1 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: #378ADD; top: -150px; right: -100px; }
    .hero__blob--2 { width: 350px; height: 350px; background: #185fa5; bottom: -100px; left: -50px; }

    .hero__content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(55,138,221,0.2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(55,138,221,0.4);
      color: #7ec8f7;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7ec8f7, #378ADD);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn--primary { background: #378ADD; color: #fff; }
    .btn--primary:hover { background: #185fa5; }
    .btn--outline { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); color: #fff; }
    .btn--outline:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

    .stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat__num { display: block; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: #7ec8f7; }
    .stat__label { font-size: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.6; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(55,138,221,0.1);
    }

    .card {
      padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #001c47;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(55,138,221,0.1);
      transition: background 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .card:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .card:hover { background: rgba(55,138,221,0.04); }

    .card__icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .card p { font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.65; line-height: 1.6; flex: 1; }
    .card__cta { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #378ADD; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
      .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .card { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(55,138,221,0.1); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="header">
    <img src="/demo-docs/logo.svg" alt="GMONIT" />
    <span>Документация</span>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__grid"></div>
    <div class="hero__blob hero__blob--1"></div>
    <div class="hero__blob hero__blob--2"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <div class="badge">Observability платформа</div>
      <h1>Видите всё.<br/><span class="gradient">Реагируете первыми.</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">GMONIT — единая платформа мониторинга приложений, инфраструктуры и бизнес-процессов с AI-детекцией аномалий.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/demo-docs/getting-started/quickstart" class="btn btn--primary">Начать работу →</a>
        <a href="https://gmonit.ru" target="_blank" class="btn btn--outline">О продукте ↗</a>
      </div>
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">15+</span><span class="stat__label">технологий</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">&lt;1 мин</span><span class="stat__label">до первых данных</span></div>
        <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">AI</span><span class="stat__label">детекция аномалий</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cards">
    <a href="/demo-docs/agents/apm" class="card">
      <div class="card__icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>APM</h3>
      <p>Мониторинг производительности приложений. Java, Python, Node.js, Go и другие.</p>
      <span class="card__cta">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo-docs/agents/infra" class="card">
      <div class="card__icon">🖥️</div>
      <h3>Инфраструктура</h3>
      <p>Серверы, базы данных, очереди сообщений — всё в одном месте.</p>
      <span class="card__cta">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo-docs/agents/rum" class="card">
      <div class="card__icon">🌐</div>
      <h3>Браузер и мобайл</h3>
      <p>Real User Monitoring — видите опыт каждого пользователя в реальном времени.</p>
      <span class="card__cta">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/demo-docs/use-cases" class="card">
      <div class="card__icon">🤖</div>
      <h3>AI аномалии</h3>
      <p>Предиктивное выявление проблем до того как они влияют на бизнес.</p>
      <span class="card__cta">Подробнее →</span>
    </a>
  </section>

</body>
</html>